<P>But usually when they have occasion to speak of many they express themselves by <HI>Numerals</HI> set after the <HI>Noun</HI>; as <HI>Dissawva</HI> two, three, <HI>&amp;c. An Egg, Bittera, Eggs, Bittera cattei,</HI> word for word, <HI>Egg many.</HI></P>
