<P>I shall only make one Observation from these words, and that is concerning the four first. It is this, that they have no words of their own Language for <HI>God</HI> and <HI>Heaven,</HI> but in all probability borrowed them from the <HI>Portugueze.</HI> But for the two next, <HI>The Devil</HI> and <HI>Hell,</HI> words of their own. They number thus,
